<figureCitation box="[838,927,1179,1203]" captionStart="Figure 48" captionStartId="18.[192,276,1160,1182]" captionTargetBox="[192,1440,192,1128]" captionTargetId="figure-57@18.[192,1440,192,1128]" captionTargetPageId="18" captionText="Figure 48. Gravel bar habitat at Nerepis River, Queens Co., Bayard, NB, habitat for Hydrosmecta caduca Casey, H. canadensis Webster and Klimaszewski, sp. nov. (type locality),H. dulcis Casey, andH. minutissimoides Webster and Klimaszewski, sp. nov. (type locality)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5169567" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5169567/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="8">Fig. 48</figureCitation>
